subject: Soccer
Women's World Cup (Soccer)
lead_paragraph: Nigeria overcame deficits of 2-0 and 3-2 to forge a tie with fifth-ranked Sweden, and Cameroon scored three goals in nine minutes in a rout of Ecuador.
